SUMMARY:Little Coyotes Forest Kinder Open House
DESCRIPTION:Davis Forest School’s all-outdoors preschool/kinder program for 3-6 year olds gives children the opportunity to learn and play in the rhythm of the seasons\, while building friendships\, resilience\, and a deep sense of belonging in nature. Like we often say\, children have the rest of their lives to be indoors\, so let’s keep these early years wild and in connection with the land. \nFor the 2026-2027 school year\, we are excited to offer all five days (Monday-Fridays) in Davis and Sacramento. Families will have the flexibility to choose which days work best for their families. We are also delighted to share that we will have a Folsom location for Little Coyotes this upcoming year! \nJoin us for one of our three upcoming Open Houses\, where we’ll welcome new families\, walk the land together\, and share the heart of our work. The Open Houses will be on: \n-Saturday\, February 21st from 11:00am-12:30pm in Davis\n-Saturday\, February 28th from 11:00am-12:30pm in Sacramento\n-Saturday\, March 7th from 11:00am-12:30pm in Folsom \nPlease fill out the brief RSVP form to let us know which Open House you are interested in joining. As we get closer to the Open House date you select\, we will reach out to your family with more information. \nDavis Forest School’s website is: https://davisforestschool.org/programs/littlecoyotes/
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/little-coyotes-forest-kinder-open-house-3/
LOCATION:Folsom Lake
CATEGORIES:Bring the Kids,Community
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-22-at-1.11.10-PM.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Davis Forest School":MAILTO:programs@davisforestschool.org
END:VEVENT
