SUMMARY:Get Sauced Pasta PopUp
DESCRIPTION:The Pasta Exchange’s Get Sauced popup at Davis Wine Bar returns Saturday 1/31 and will continue through winter & spring on Saturday nights moving forward. Reservations are available via our websites below… \nwww.thepastaexchange.com\nwww.daviswinebar.com\nBook a table at The Pasta Exchange\nthe-pasta-exchange.resos.com \nWe’ve updated the menu with fresh new pastas. Look for Linguine & Clams and Baked Rigatoni Bolognese on the menu as well as Roasted Artichokes with Tahini~Yogurt Sauce for the veggie lovers out there. \nLook for The Pasta Exchange showing up more often in Downtown Davis at Davis Wine Bar!
