SUMMARY:Showing of the film "Sudan\, Remember Us"
DESCRIPTION:Davis Friends are asking people to come and learn about this over-looked war in Sudan. The media does not focus on the Sudan war because the Ukraine and Gaza conflicts are of much greater western strategic interest. The lack of media coverage and reliable information has contributed to the greatest humanitarian crisis in the world today as millions face famine and displacement. This program is co-sponsored by Woodland for Peace. Admission is free and light snacks and beverages will be provided.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/showing-of-the-film-sudan-remember-us/
LOCATION:Friends Meetinghouse\, 345 L St\, Davis\, 345 L St\, Davis\, CA\, 95616
CATEGORIES:Screen
ORGANIZER;CN="Davis Friends Meeting (Quaker)":MAILTO:info@davisfriendsmeeting.org
END:VEVENT
